Many residents of the Soutpansberg mourn the death of Mr Hector Mackay Kincaid-Smith. He passed away after a long illness on 16 August at the age of 76 years.  Kinciad-Smith, who lived in the area for many years, moved to Durban with his loving wife Hazel in January this year. He will be sadly missed by Hazel and children Jessica and Dane.